Package: metacapa
Title: Metapopulation Capacity-based Conservation Prioritization
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Matthew", "Strimas-Mackey", email = "mstrimas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8929-7776"))
Description:
  Tools for calculating Hanski and Ovaskainen's (2000) metapopulation capcity, 
  a relative metric of metapopulation persistence, and performing 
  persistence-based conservation prioritization based on this metric.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
